whole_object: This park is so popular, even the benches are always taken—talk about taking a stand, or in this case, a seat!
single_object:
- Fountain: This fountain, a splash hit with the local birds, clearly has the best liquid assets in town.
- Benches: If you're feeling benched by life, just remember, every good rest deserves a pause.
- Trees: Leaf it to these trees to make sure everyone gets a fair shade of attention.
- Building: This building's story is quite a tall tale - it's floors above the rest!
- Walkway: This walkway is always on the right path, leading pedestrians to their destination one step at a time.
- Lamp posts: By night, these lamp posts really know how to light up a room – outdoor edition.
- Grass: This grass may just be a blade in the field of green, but it's outstanding in its own turf.
- Bridge: The bridge always thought it could span new horizons; turns out it’s quite an overachiever.
